rt004&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7320360" target="_blank"&gt;@新窮A&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31970371&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=120512183868630ba85fd3b6_01476325"/><published>2025-06-30T21:22:51+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2da27b4f3a3d488b7b05f66a90c43f11</id><title>移英港人變晒林超英</title><updated>2025-07-01T00:34:22+08:00</updated><author><name>2006Win-Cat</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-01T00:34:22+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573055983"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573055983"&gt;有移英港人在社交平台threads發文表示，「呢幾日英國南部上到三十度，屋企無冷氣嘅移英港人變晒林超英」；又指自己在家中工作猶如地獄，「我WFH所以一到夏天就work from hell」。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31970487&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=120512183868630ba85fd3b6_01476325"/><published>2025-07-01T00:34:22+08:00</published></entry></feed>